OK, so all political
correctness aside,

00:09:05.176 --> 00:09:06.550
I'm going to use
this opportunity

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:09.430
to tell you that you have
been one of my biggest

00:09:09.430 --> 00:09:11.680
