looks of an actor,

00:09:28.330 --> 00:09:30.700
and there is a y-axis
that shows you the--

00:09:30.700 --> 00:09:33.130
ARJUN RAMPAL: Are we talking
Silicon Valley language?

00:09:33.130 --> 00:09:33.460
I don't understand.

00:09:33.460 --> 00:09:34.376
APRAJITA JAIN: No, no.

00:09:34.376 --> 00:09:37.020
I'm just talking basic maths.

00:09:37.020 --> 00:09:39.580
So let's say there's
looks over here

00:09:39.580 --> 00:09:41.890
and superior acting skills here.

00:09:41.890 --> 00:09:43.630
You'll find many
Bollywood stars that

00:09:43.630 --> 00:09:45.820
are on the far bottom right--

00:09:45.820 --> 00:09:48.970
great looking-- and you'll
find many that are on the left

00:09:48.970 --> 00:09:50.080
corner there--

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.600
amazing acting skills, but
so-so in the looks department.

00:09:52.600 --> 00:09:55.870
You for me are on
the up and the right

00:09:55.870 --> 00:09:58.100
that covers both these areas.

00:09:58.100 --> 00:10:00.850
So with this versatility
and you know,

00:10:00.850 --> 00:10:04.900
being a fantastic actor as well
as jaw-droppingly good looking,

00:10:04.900 --> 00:10:06.490
tell me a little
bit more about--

00:10:06.490 --> 00:10:07.240
and we know a lot about it--

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:09.364
ARJUN RAMPAL: It sounds
like a great app, you know?

00:10:09.364 --> 00:10:10.698
Just now, I mean, what she said.

