00:16:06.350 --> 00:16:08.945
I'm sure a lot of your
boys will agree with me.

00:16:08.945 --> 00:16:10.850
Do you agree with me,
a lot of you guys?

00:16:10.850 --> 00:16:12.440
You like that
gangster film, right?

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:14.411
I mean, you want to
play that one gangster.

00:16:14.411 --> 00:16:16.160
And there have been
so many gangster films

00:16:16.160 --> 00:16:19.475
that have been made, like
"The Godfather," "Goodfellas,"

00:16:19.475 --> 00:16:26.840
"Scarface," you know, "Satya,"
[INAUDIBLE],, "Company," really

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:28.700
good films that have come out.

00:16:28.700 --> 00:16:32.590
And I was wondering,
now, who could I play?

00:16:32.590 --> 00:16:35.720
And there were these
guys who came up

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:38.720
