the gap between that.

00:53:53.275 --> 00:53:59.970
I think women's safety today
is on everybody's mind.

00:53:59.970 --> 00:54:01.770
I have two daughters.

00:54:01.770 --> 00:54:07.250
I want India to be the safest
place in the world for women.

00:54:07.250 --> 00:54:09.740
And I think that's
something which one really

00:54:09.740 --> 00:54:11.080
